Just over a month ago, on 30 March, the number of #CoronaVirus cases:
Karnataka: 83
Maharashtra: 198. That's 2.38 times.

Today evening, the number of cases:
Karnataka: 576
Maharashtra: 10,498. That's 18.23 times.
